name: Yiffy TotesFleisch8 Finetune
description:
Model's aim is to be able to imitate tf8 artstyle. Please don't use this model to impersonate tf8, or to sell work that is a close imitation of his.

Trained on top of Yiffy e18 with batch size 40 on a dataset of approximately 1200 images downloaded from e621. This was trained on top of my shark model so it is capable of doing good sharks.
